---
<section class="adv-section">
 <div class="adv-container">
 
 <!-- Top Section -->
 <div class="adv-top">
 <div class="adv-top-text">
 <h4 class="adv-subtitle">THE MULHOLLAND ADVANTAGE</h4>
 <h2 class="adv-title">We do both — gates and<br/>fences, <span class="adv-title-blue">under one roof</span></h2>
 
 <p class="adv-desc">
 Most homeowners hire one contractor for their fence and a completely separate company for their gate. This often leads to mismatched colors, conflicting metal profiles, and multiple contractors pointing fingers at each other.
 </p>
 <p class="adv-desc">
 Because Mulholland Brand is a full-service manufacturer and installer of both gates and fences, we ensure a flawless, coordinated design across your entire property. Even if you start with just a fence or just a gate today, we engineer our systems so they can be perfectly expanded and matched in the future.
 </p>
 </div>
 <div class="adv-top-img-wrapper">
 <picture>
 <source media="(max-width: 1024px)" srcset="/assets/images/the-advantage/movil/The%20Mulholland%20Advantage%20M.jpg" />
 <img src="/assets/images/the-advantage/We do both gates and fences, under one roof1.webp" alt="House with gate" class="adv-top-img" />
 </picture>
 </div>
 </div>

 <!-- Primary Banner -->
 <div class="adv-blue-bar">
 <div class="adv-btn-container">
 <!-- Desktop CTA -->
 <a href="#estimate" class="adv-btn adv-btn-desktop">
 <span class="adv-btn-white">Request Free On-Site Estimate</span>
 <img src="/assets/images/icon_phone.svg" alt="Phone" class="adv-btn-icon" />
 <span class="adv-btn-gold">Or Call Now: (800) 562-5770</span>
 </a>
 <!-- Mobile CTA -->
 <a href="#estimate" class="adv-btn adv-btn-mobile">
 <span class="adv-btn-white">Request Free On-Site Estimate</span>
 </a>
 <a href="tel:8005625770" class="adv-btn adv-btn-mobile">
 <img src="/assets/images/icon_phone.svg" alt="Phone" class="adv-btn-icon" />
 <span class="adv-btn-gold">Or Call Now: (800) 562-5770</span>
 </a>
 </div>
 </div>

 <!-- Bottom Section -->
 <div class="adv-bottom">
 <div class="adv-bottom-img-wrapper">
 <picture>
 <source media="(max-width: 1024px)" srcset="/assets/images/the-advantage/movil/The%20Mulholland%20Advantage-M.jpg" />
 <img src="/assets/images/the-advantage/We do both gates and fences, under one roof2.webp" alt="Modern fence" class="adv-bottom-img" />
 </picture>
 </div>
 
 <div class="adv-features-grid">
 <div class="adv-feature">
 <img src="/assets/images/the-advantage/One trusted local team.svg" alt="Local Team" class="adv-icon" />
 <h3 class="adv-feature-title">One trusted local team</h3>
 <p class="adv-feature-text">A single point of contact from design to installation — no finger-pointing between contractors.</p>
 </div>
 
 <div class="adv-feature">
 <img src="/assets/images/the-advantage/Perfectly coordinated design.svg" alt="Coordinated Design" class="adv-icon" />
 <h3 class="adv-feature-title">Perfectly coordinated design</h3>
 <p class="adv-feature-text">Matching colors and metal profiles across your gates and fencing, every time.</p>
 </div>
 
 <div class="adv-feature">
 <img src="/assets/images/the-advantage/One comprehensive warranty.svg" alt="Comprehensive Warranty" class="adv-icon" />
 <h3 class="adv-feature-title">One comprehensive warranty</h3>
 <p class="adv-feature-text">Your entire perimeter system is covered under a single, unified warranty.</p>
 </div>
 
 <div class="adv-feature">
 <img src="/assets/images/the-advantage/Built to expand.svg" alt="Built to expand" class="adv-icon" />
 <h3 class="adv-feature-title">Built to expand</h3>
 <p class="adv-feature-text">Start with a fence or a gate today — we engineer systems to match and grow later.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

 </div>
</section>

<style>
 .adv-section {
 width: 100%;
 background-color: #ffffff;
 display: flex;
 justify-content: center;
 padding: 71px 20px 0 20px;
 }

 .adv-container {
 width: 100%;
 max-width: 1421px; 
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 /* Optional border if it was in the design, but omitted to be clean */
 }

 /* ─── TOP BLOCK ────────────────────────────────────────── */
 .adv-top {
 display: flex;
 margin-bottom: 0;
 }

 .adv-top-text {
 flex: 1;
 padding: 60px 40px 60px 0; /* Right padding */
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 justify-content: center;
 text-align: left;
 }

 .adv-subtitle {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 600; /* Bold */
 font-size: 12px;
 line-height: 16px;
 letter-spacing: 2.64px;
 color: #2C65B0;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 margin-bottom: 20px;
 }

 .adv-title {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 800; /* Bold */
 font-size: 45px;
 line-height: 45px;
 letter-spacing: -0.94px;
 color: #14110E;
 margin: 0 0 30px 0;
 }

 .adv-title-blue {
 color: #2C65B0;
 }

 .adv-desc {
 font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; /* fallback */
 font-weight: 400;
 font-size: 16px;
 line-height: 26px;
 color: #635C57;
 margin-bottom: 20px;
 }

 .adv-desc:last-child {
 margin-bottom: 0;
 }

 .adv-top-img-wrapper {
 flex: 1.1; 
 display: flex;
 }

 .adv-top-img {
 width: 100%;
 height: 100%;
 object-fit: cover;
 display: block;
 }

 /* ─── BLUE BAR ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
 .adv-blue-bar {
 width: 100%;
 height: 105px;
 background-color: #2C65B0;
 display: flex;
 align-items: center;
 justify-content: center;
 }

 .adv-btn-container {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 gap: 10px;
 width: 100%;
 align-items: center;
 padding: 0 20px;
 }

 .adv-btn {
 width: 100%;
 max-width: 715px;
 height: 56px;
 border-radius: 45px;
 background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);
 display: flex;
 align-items: center;
 justify-content: center;
 text-decoration: none;
 gap: 15px;
 transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
 }

 .adv-btn:hover {
 background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
 }

 .adv-btn-white {
 font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; /* Fallback for button text */
 font-size: 16px;
 color: #ffffff;
 font-weight: 600;
 }

 .adv-btn-gold {
 font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
 font-size: 16px;
 color: #EAC848;
 font-weight: 600;
 }

 .adv-btn-icon {
 width: 20px;
 height: auto;
 }

 .adv-btn-desktop {
 display: flex;
 }

 .adv-btn-mobile {
 display: none;
 }

 /* ─── BOTTOM BLOCK ─────────────────────────────────────── */
 .adv-bottom {
 display: flex;
 }

 .adv-bottom-img-wrapper {
 flex: 1.1;
 display: flex;
 }

 .adv-bottom-img {
 width: 100%;
 height: 100%;
 object-fit: cover;
 display: block;
 }

 .adv-features-grid {
 flex: 1;
 display: grid;
 grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
 gap: 40px;
 padding: 60px 0 60px 60px; /* Padding inside the text block */
 }

 .adv-feature {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 align-items: flex-start;
 }

 .adv-icon {
 height: 40px; /* Roughly scale */
 width: auto;
 margin-bottom: 20px;
 }

 .adv-feature-title {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 800; /* Bold */
 font-size: 26px;
 line-height: 24px;
 color: #14110E;
 margin: 0 0 15px 0;
 text-align: left;
 display: flex;
 align-items: center;
 min-height: 48px;
 }

 .adv-feature-text {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 400; /* Regular */
 font-size: 14px;
 line-height: 23px;
 color: #635C57;
 margin: 0;
 text-align: left;
 }

 /* ─── RESPONSIVE ───────────────────────────────────────── */
 @media (max-width: 768px) {
  .adv-section {
  padding-top: 54px !important;
  padding-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  .adv-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  }

  .adv-top {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  order: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .adv-top-text {
  display: contents; 
  }

  .adv-subtitle {
  order: 1;
  font-size: 12px !important;
  line-height: 16px !important;
  letter-spacing: 2.64px !important;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 25px !important;
  width: 100%;
  }

  .adv-title {
  order: 2;
  font-size: 24px !important;
  line-height: 27px !important;
  letter-spacing: -0.9px !important;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 30px !important;
  width: 100%;
  }

  .adv-top-img-wrapper {
  order: 3;
  width: calc(100% + 40px) !important;
  margin-left: -20px !important;
  margin-right: -20px !important;
  height: auto !important;
  margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  .adv-top-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  object-fit: cover;
  }

  .adv-desc {
  order: 4;
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-weight: 400 !important;
  font-size: 14px !important;
  line-height: 20px !important;
  color: #635C57 !important;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 0 10px;
  margin-bottom: 20px !important;
  }
  
  p.adv-desc:first-of-type {
  margin-top: 35px !important;
  }

  p.adv-desc:last-of-type {
  margin-bottom: 35px !important;
  }

  .adv-bottom {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  order: 2;
  }

  .adv-bottom-img-wrapper {
  order: 1;
  width: calc(100% + 40px) !important;
  margin-left: -20px !important;
  margin-right: -20px !important;
  height: auto !important;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .adv-bottom-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  object-fit: cover;
  }

  .adv-features-grid {
  order: 2;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  padding: 0 10px 40px 10px;
  gap: 20px;
  }

  .adv-feature {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  }

  .adv-icon[alt="Local Team"] { width: 44px !important; height: 44px !important; margin-bottom: 15px !important; }
  .adv-icon[alt="Coordinated Design"] { width: 40.38px !important; height: 40.38px !important; margin-bottom: 15px !important; }
  .adv-icon[alt="Comprehensive Warranty"] { width: 36.34px !important; height: 40.88px !important; margin-bottom: 15px !important; }
  .adv-icon[alt="Built to expand"] { width: 41.39px !important; height: 40.38px !important; margin-bottom: 15px !important; }

  .adv-feature-title {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-weight: 800 !important;
  font-size: 17px !important;
  line-height: 15.7px !important;
  color: #14110E !important;
  text-align: center !important;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: flex-start !important;
  margin-bottom: 15px !important;
  min-height: 35px !important;
  white-space: normal !important; 
  }

  .adv-feature-text {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-weight: 400 !important;
  font-size: 12px !important;
  line-height: 16px !important;
  text-align: center !important;
  }

  .adv-blue-bar {
  order: 3;
  width: calc(100% + 40px) !important;
  margin-left: -20px !important;
  margin-right: -20px !important;
  height: 52px !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
  border-radius: 0 !important;
  background-color: #2C65B0 !important;
  }

  .adv-btn-desktop {
  display: flex !important;
  background: transparent !important;
  border-radius: 0 !important;
  height: 52px !important;
  width: 100% !important;
  justify-content: center !important;
  gap: 5px !important;
  }

  .adv-btn-mobile {
  display: none !important;
  }

  .adv-btn-white {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-size: 10px !important;
  font-weight: 600 !important;
  line-height: 18px !important;
  color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  .adv-btn-gold {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-size: 10px !important;
  font-weight: 600 !important;
  line-height: 18px !important;
  color: #EAC848 !important;
  }

  .adv-btn-icon {
  width: 12.16px !important;
  height: 12.16px !important;
  }
  }
</style>
